Title: Nerdcore is Dead(?)
Presenters: YTCracker, Steffo, StarF, King Pheenix, 2 Mello, Devo Spice
Book Description: 'Nerdcore hip-hop is often taken as a parody genre.  With 'nerdy' references sneaking into more and more mainstream music- is 'nerd rap' a stale term?  Join some of the top artists as they debate the validity of their own genre.'

Title: Do Angry Fans Ruin It?
Presenters: StarF, Val Hundreds, Moses Jackson, James Fernandez, BluRaven C. Houvener
Book Description: 'Was Mass Effect 3 improved by the outrage of gamers? Do TV shows like Community or Top Gear need angry feedback- or are we encouraging authors- artists and designers to be less creative to avoid fan ire?  Is sequel-itis all our fault?'
